Collophore (
Figs 31–33
). Anterior side with two large and three small ciliate chaetae (
Fig 31
); posterior side with one large apical and three small subapical smooth chaetae (
Fig. 32
); lateral flap with about nine smooth chaetae (
Fig. 33
